                      MP (THRIFT) GLOBAL ADVISERS III LLC
                    

•   NEW YORK, NY
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             MP (thrift) Global Advisers III is based out of New York.   Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $1,003,574,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 100.0%. MP (thrift) Global Advisers III's largest holding is Flagstar Bancorp Inc with shares held of 35,600,352.   WhaleWisdom has at least 30 13F filings in our database for MP (thrift) Global Advisers III. 
                                           














